警處理。<br />\n<br />\n警員到場向一名姓劉（50歲）男子盤查，期間有人不合作，最後將他拘捕及帶返警署進一步調查，證實他是一名休班警務人員，他已被暫控一項盜竊及阻礙警務人員執行職務罪，今日（7日）在觀塘裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n警隊重申非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又黎，高層震怒？"},{"pid":"545fd44887e43feee60c71b77d464a1cb324f779","tid":1142164,"uid":60655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T02:06:35.000Z","msg":"呀sir囉衫唔洗你教"},{"pid":"211849820c0615f58d31a6e5b684ef623d0f6144","tid":1142164,"uid":27529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T02:08:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4278d3c2cb866d7f308c9106aeb9d72720dd3a41","tid":1142164,"uid":61545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T02:17:53.000Z","msg":"台灣風化案最多<br />\n香港就休班警系列最多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"510383ac1a55f94de4d84e806ac55546f705aae8","tid":1142164,"uid":73492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T02:55:05.000Z","msg":"其實點解會咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n貪污食埋黑社會條糧都仲明白<br />\n偷一舊水既衫無左份幾萬蚊既工<br />\n弱智架？"},{"pid":"426b13fe49ca60c598870e40412e0b53a4be3a0d","tid":1142164,"uid":4420,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"510383ac1a55f94de4d84e806ac55546f705aae8","tid":1142164,"uid":73492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T02:55:05.000Z","msg":"其實點解會咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n貪污食埋黑社會條糧都仲明白<br />\n偷一舊水既衫無左份幾萬蚊既工<br />\n弱智架？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T02:58:44.000Z","msg":"最重要果樣呢<br />\n過百萬長俸冇埋"},{"pid":"e10202812078901da8a0dcac3ecea0423c9474ba","tid":1142164,"uid":43314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"426b13fe49ca60c598870e40412e0b53a4be3a0d","tid":1142164,"uid":4420,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"510383ac1a55f94de4d84e806ac55546f705aae8","tid":1142164,"uid":73492,"like":0,"dislike":0,